To build and run A5, execute the following
    $ cd A5/
    $ premake4 gmake
    $ make
    $ cd Assets
    $ ../A5 <lua_script>


----

All extra features can be turn on and off using `options.hpp`

1: Extra primitives(triangular prism, triangular pyramid)
2: Reflection
3: Refraction
4: Glossy reflection
5: Glossy refraction
6: Soft shadows
7: Depth of field
8: Motion blur
9: Final Scene
10: Acceleration(bounding volume hierarchy)

tested on mechine gl41
